# Simple Chat app

## Backend

Full API documentation can be found in docs/API.md

## Running tests

The test suite is set up using tox.

    tox

## Running the server

### Bootstrap the server

    cd backend/chat/
    virtualenv env -p python3
    source env/bin/activate
    pip install -r requirements.txt

### Run the server

    ./manage.py runserver

### Main Technologies

* Python 3
* Django 1.10
* Django Rest Framework
